# House Price Prediction Lab3

## Overview
This lab analyzes a House Price dataset using Python. The goal is to explore the data and build a regression model to predict house prices.

## Objective
To understand the factors affecting house prices and develop a predictive model.

## Steps
- Data cleaning and preprocessing
- Exploratory Data Analysis (EDA)
- Data visualization
- Correlation analysis
- Regression modeling


## Objective
To understand the factors affecting house prices and develop a predictive model.
